.DT
do_busy
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
do_busy

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
do_busy -  This method handles setting the busy flag.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int do_busy(string str)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^str%^RESET%^ - the on or off string
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/events.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method handles setting the busy flag.  The busy flag can only
be set by liaisons and lords, why lords?  Just because :)  This
command was inspired by moonchild.
.EP

